sudoku.model

Class IntelligentSudokuCell

  • java.lang.Object
    • sudoku.model.IntelligentSudokuCell
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    class IntelligentSudokuCell
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    An intelligent cell of a Sudoku board that can tell its remaining possibilities, if it's set or not, its content to other objects and can be cloned.
